@startuml watch_mode
title Watch Mode

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Core" as bausteinsicht_cli_core
participant "Watcher" as bausteinsicht_watcher
participant "Engine" as bausteinsicht_sync_engine

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 1. bausteinsicht watch
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_watcher : 2. Start(model.jsonc, arch.drawio)
bausteinsicht_watcher -> bausteinsicht_watcher : 3. on file change: debounce 300ms
bausteinsicht_watcher -> bausteinsicht_sync_engine : 4. Run(model, document, state, templates, opts)
bausteinsicht_sync_engine --> bausteinsicht_watcher : 5. SyncResult
bausteinsicht_watcher --> architect : 6. Log + display summary of changes
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 7. Ctrl+C
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_watcher : 8. Stop()

@enduml
